<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Four killed in explosion at Oryx mine.</title>
<headline>Four killed in explosion at Oryx mine.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-03-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>Oryx Gold Mine said on Monday that four contract employees had been killed in an explosion at the mine on Saturday morning.</p>
<p>It said the explosion, the cause of which was not known with certainty, occurred in the 18 level return airway some 1,800 metres below the surface.</p>
<p>The incident was being investigated, it said.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom, +27 11 482 1003</p>
